Diversity Matters at Collette

 

Collette is proud to be an equal opportunity employer. We embrace our differences and believe that a diverse workforce is vital to our success as a global organization.  All hiring decisions are based on qualifications, competence and business need.  We are committed to providing a diverse and inclusive work environment and do not discriminate against any status protected under law.
